Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是在朦胧之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}涌出的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无暇整理自己的心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我与学姐相识
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过一日而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么不能说出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说“为什么”我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你怎么可能当我恋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为你又比我小还戴眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这么瘦弱而且戴着眼镜又爱妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}咦 眼镜出现了两次？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还很色情 以自我为中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别再妄想了啊 我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前略 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不肖顽弟上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}令弟痴狂顽劣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}终猝死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不成器 歉之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}耻留于世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}起床了 海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再不起来上学就要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃早餐的时间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“我今天休息”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}出什么事了吗？海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道说身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身体没有异状？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学 海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“请不要管我 海人”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“我今天休息”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“请不要管我”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说我这样放着他不管好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说回来为什么口都不愿意开要递纸条来说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道说这是什么暗号…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是有趣啊 一夏你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我搞错什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个啊 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是普通的偷懒逃学而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偷懒逃学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是说雾岛他有不想来学校的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如不想读书啊 不想看到某人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想…看到？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天晚上 发生什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什…什么都没发生…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然有诡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}年轻真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你还记得昨天的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…大家在一起说电影的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后 干杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再然后玩扑克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到这里都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可这是之后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知什么时候就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}醒来头就好疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}究竟是为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哟 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你还记得昨天发生了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀…我也不太记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了对了 我上学的时候碰到柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她要我把这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行不行不行！不能看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说不能看就是不能看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了啊 昨天的我到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 大家到位子上坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在开早会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}首先 由于雾岛同学身体不适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以今天缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天还挺精神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家也要好好注意身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 现在点一下名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}相川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是因为…知道了我的真实身份了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你不是这个星球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个人是外星人！超可怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快来拯救地球啊 黑衣人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(765,658)}Men in Black
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}出自一部关于外星人的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}救命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不要当实验体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}更不要解剖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多么…吓人的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过究竟该如何跟海人说明好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是该和他坦白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可那时候海人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐她现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶！？被海人告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 昨天晚上突然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后你怎么回答的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当然是NO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人真是不知道自己有几斤几两
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也许他心里很虚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还不如说是没脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我脑子里会冒出这么不吉利的妄想来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}干嘛啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 你们不去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说去是去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去探望海人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他现在不舒服着呢 过去只是添乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不好他肚子正饿着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐在那里 肯定好生伺候着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是一夏学姐肯定把海人照顾得服服贴贴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贴身扶腰哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}第一話出現過的neta 手取り足取り的誤用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来擦脸脸咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里也得周到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从后面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从前面来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱 我想起来我有急事先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…柑菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪儿一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 这样好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样…好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为…哲朗你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是个机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去是…去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 8mm摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是学姐的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就猜到可能会有这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像能拍到很“真实”的场景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管什么时候人都是会饿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是叫什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也要吃点什么不？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快递吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷…谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个我…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我没说清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她也没回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以别笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}脸很红哦 身体还不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我稍微睡了一下就舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说谎不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实我今天是逃学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 这样让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我已经放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是来看我的吧 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}站着说话不方便  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 昨天才向我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天就带另一个女生回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人真是肉食动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒不如说是杂食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…现在去哪逛逛不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你突然怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 可以是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去换下衣服 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要…要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很久没去轻井泽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顺便为电影采外景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么 要出门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学不是生病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 要上了哦 Snake
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}出自一款叫做合金装备的潜入游戏 男主角的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就这样不回去…去别的地方的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…姐姐拜托我了要照顾好海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人和谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐不是地球人啊 是外星人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}救命 快来拯救地球啊 黑衣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}听得到吗 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托了 用连环让我跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(648,660)}linkage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么毫无反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人…人挺多的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毕竟是七月的星期六嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪里采外景？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有仔细考虑过  就这么逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就闲逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像在约会一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 人这么多不方便摄影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这种程度的准备是起码的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这叫起码吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}青春的光辉稍瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要留下它的倩影必须付出各种努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 我有点口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去买点果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑到哪里去了啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉…要你陪我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事啦 反正我也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是大杯一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学为什么没去学校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不是显而易见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为贵月学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也许 这都请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但这对柑菜来说却是个好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会被踢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}妨碍别人的恋情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}日语俗语妨碍别人恋情会被马踢死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我有妨碍吗  我可是在支持哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我懂得的 是妨碍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗会被踢的 被自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且…那大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多谢你为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 那是美樱你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜对我而言只是一起长大的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦哦 真是不错的景致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找到适合的地方了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你啊 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没问我为什么逃学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很在意…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你不想说的话 就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是因为学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是说有什么特别的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}实际上 真的什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然啊 要突然和别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且是女孩子一起住 还是有不少得注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐毕竟是个美女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…身材也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是比我年长 而且又是外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能会有很多观念上的差异
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想到这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}挺温柔的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？柠檬学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在…做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃…怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太过追求画面的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}忘记躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你！在！拍！什！么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}青春无敌思春少女所做的稚嫩的告白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你别说些莫名其妙的话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这可是偷拍哦！偷拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}赤裸裸的犯罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说今天早上的照片是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把那个样子的我偷拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个样子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我和学姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然跑了 学姐站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 跑到哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找了你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么连美樱你们都在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}额…这是柠檬学姐说要我们帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明是你自己要跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是柠檬学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 不是的…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们这些大坏蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才的声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学…学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有事…要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊……！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么要追我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是有原因的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也有原因啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海他去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是已经回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是可惜啊 谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你笑什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么追到这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说原因…到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天 海人同学要说的那些话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是和我有关吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果被人知道的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会很糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…看情况也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看吧 肯定会！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不能继续在海人家住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个地方也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实也没必要非得搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然多少会有点尴尬…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没想到会让你那么为难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这件事就放在海人心里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不要跟大家说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？怎么可能说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很丢人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}丢人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有那么丢人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是被拒绝了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你觉得我昨天是想说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以说那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不可告人的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有这样的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天海人是想说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可告人的秘密是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}耍赖…先回答我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果学姐说的话我也说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的不知道吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天一天都还没吃过东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们都没提到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只说了一些不痛不痒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如兴趣…喜欢的食物什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了我们还仅仅是这样的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总感觉心里却变得轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擅自拍摄可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正以后也要拍很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…朝这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗨 海人同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}除了昨天的事 我还有事要问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你究竟是被谁拒绝了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是谁是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有被谁拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…有没有喜欢的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是谷川同学吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天也在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…是北原同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都说了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难不成是我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开…玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A君向B酱告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Amy酱向B太君…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}C酱有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底谁是谁阿 搞不清了
